body:
# lol-tournament-code-project

5v5 Matching system

A program, where people can find other 9 people that speak the same language and roughly the same skill and where they can play a 5v5 against each other while being in TeamSpeak for communication and tactics.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
